{"tid":2153739,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"佛教反唔反對占卜算命？","createTime":"2020-08-12T17:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T14:23:46.000Z","uid":37397,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"54b8179cf0fb3bda968e1a0aac66e7438218f872","tid":2153739,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:07:52.000Z","msg":"邪命：為了貪求利養，為他人占卜算命。<br />\n&ldquo;吉凶者，得失之象也&rdquo;。有&ldquo;得&rdquo;，為&ldquo;吉&rdquo;﹔有&ldquo;失&rdquo;，為&ldquo;凶&rdquo;。而其實&ldquo;吉&rdquo;與&ldquo;凶&rdquo;都是由於前世善惡之因，而所享受的&ldquo;得&rdquo;與&ldquo;失&rdquo;的果報。可惜世俗人只講趨吉避凶，不講因果報應。放下分別執著，便無須再以命理風水等來&ldquo;趨吉避凶&rdquo;！<br />\n<br />\n係咪姐係反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1bb87d9aa01ce704d3e94c2a0a4d737829fc87","tid":2153739,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:19:42.000Z","msg":"天機不可泄漏"},{"pid":"8e69d0523fad20c23484a9f0ee87129875d4f1e6","tid":2153739,"uid":269044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4c1bb87d9aa01ce704d3e94c2a0a4d737829fc87","tid":2153739,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:19:42.000Z","msg":"天機不可泄漏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:29:47.000Z","msg":"其實有講你以為自己泄露哂左天機，其實天機係不可泄露完，不可既意思係不可能,唔係不可以"},{"pid":"6d52486995957f081aea89b919b81f69a91f3927","tid":2153739,"uid":87930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:39:45.000Z","msg":"但係睇完您段嘢 自己又唔覺得係唔可以<br />\n<br />\n佢話唔贊成趨吉避凶 應為係一個唔好嘅諗法<br />\n唔會去諗因果 咁如果你真係走去占卜 都係聽吓參考吓啫  你冇去再做下一步行動去想用少啲付出去到獲到多啲「吉」咁就冇嘢 我覺得"},{"pid":"07ef7608d330851d3fdb550e26dd806727dfec51","tid":2153739,"uid":78574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:48:33.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦，佛教咁撚包容<br />\n拜神果班都話自己信佛啦"},{"pid":"51b5bfc9755c9b85af7922c557446b61e8effb12","tid":2153739,"uid":130174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T21:08:37.000Z","msg":"占察經<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vcBsMNO6NTc\" data-sr-u